11:43.620 --> 11:46.331
You can stick her with things,
and she won't cry.

11:46.373 --> 11:47.791
She doesn't hurt.

11:49.501 --> 11:51.795
Wouldn't that be nice,
never to hurt?

11:54.047 --> 11:56.758
- Yeah, I would never
let you get hurt.

12:00.970 --> 12:02.555
- Come on, Aquarius,

12:02.597 --> 12:04.474
we don't want
to get our heads chopped off.

12:06.226 --> 12:09.521
You know, pink is the color
of the Beverly Hills Hotel...

12:09.562 --> 12:13.775
- Okay.
- Jayne Mansfield's house...

12:13.817 --> 12:16.444
and my house.

12:16.486 --> 12:17.696
That's why I picked pink.

12:17.737 --> 12:19.406
<i>I came to Hollywood</i>
<i>to follow the dream.</i>

12:19.447 --> 12:22.283
I had to leave
everything behind

12:22.325 --> 12:25.954
in order to become
what I knew I needed to become.

12:25.995 --> 12:28.957
The season of change
is upon us.

12:28.998 --> 12:33.003
- Hey, candles
are a classy touch.

12:33.044 --> 12:34.671
Sets a nice vibe.

12:34.713 --> 12:36.047
- No, these are because...

12:36.089 --> 12:38.091
My asshole neighbor

12:38.133 --> 12:40.468
cut my power!

12:41.511 --> 12:43.388
I mean, she is--
whoo--

12:43.430 --> 12:46.641
evil, but no matter
what she does,

12:46.683 --> 12:47.684
she can't...

12:47.726 --> 12:49.185
Fucking hurt me

12:49.227 --> 12:52.355
