the goddamn cops!

12:54.691 --> 12:58.903
Anyway, this place
is a work in progress.

12:58.945 --> 13:01.031
I'm designing
a whole new look for it.

13:01.072 --> 13:03.158
- No, I love it.

13:03.199 --> 13:06.411
Yeah, especially
all these mirrors.

13:08.455 --> 13:09.706
Hey, is that the--

13:09.748 --> 13:12.542
- Oh, I don't let
anybody in there.

13:12.584 --> 13:14.210
That's my sanctuary.

13:15.879 --> 13:17.714
It's my cocoon.

13:17.756 --> 13:19.341
- Your cocoon?

13:19.382 --> 13:21.885
Jesus fucking--what the fuck?

13:21.926 --> 13:24.471
- That's my parrot.

