Ooh.

13:30.060 --> 13:31.811
You be nice.

13:31.853 --> 13:33.605
- Person?
- Yeah.

13:33.646 --> 13:36.566
He was here when I moved in,
so I adopted him.

13:36.608 --> 13:38.610
I called him Bird at first,
but...

13:39.944 --> 13:41.071
The more I got to know him,

13:41.112 --> 13:43.239
the more I realized
he's complex.

13:43.281 --> 13:46.409
- Oh, hey, this is...
- Marilyn.

13:46.451 --> 13:48.036
Yeah.

13:48.078 --> 13:50.330
She's my honorary mother.

13:50.372 --> 13:51.873
Since I was a little girl,

13:51.915 --> 13:54.876
I've known that fame
is my destiny.

13:54.918 --> 13:59.047
Huge, gigantic fame.

14:03.093 --> 14:04.719
Are you ready to do it?

14:04.761 --> 14:06.262
- Oh, God, yes.

14:06.304 --> 14:08.765
- Let's get famous together.

14:08.807 --> 14:11.059
I'll sing in your band,

14:11.101 --> 14:13.520
and we'll conquer the world.

14:17.440 --> 14:19.317
- So I asked her
to join my band.

14:19.359 --> 14:22.320
- So I asked him if he wanted
to play guitar in my band.

14:22.362 --> 14:26.074
- We made a pact that night
to get famous together.

14:27.784 --> 14:31.204
<i>Some weird witchy shit...</i>

14:32.497 --> 14:35.417
<i>But I was along for the ride.</i>

14:35.458 --> 14:39.546
- Marilyn needs an offering,
something personal.

14:42.632 --> 14:45.051
- It's my demo.

14:45.093 --> 14:47.178
- Marilyn loves music.

14:47.220 --> 14:48.471
It's perfect.

14:53.018 --> 14:57.230
Marilyn, you have known
sorrow and pain,

14:57.272 --> 14:58.773
and so have we,

14:58.815 --> 15:00.817
but our hearts are pure.

15:00.859 --> 15:04.779
