she dresses like a slut,

16:43.586 --> 16:46.256
but she sees herself
as innocent,

16:46.297 --> 16:47.465
and I know
what you're thinking,

16:47.507 --> 16:49.718
but it's not about that.

16:49.759 --> 16:51.845
You know, she's, like...

16:51.886 --> 16:54.014
super disciplined.

16:54.055 --> 16:56.850
